content: The very fun thing about social anxiety is that when you don't reach out to people you feel guilty and like a bad, absent friend ... but as soon as you DO interact with people, you spend the next 3 days dwelling on how  annoying you were & how they probably hate you now.
renderedContent: The very fun thing about social anxiety is that when you don't reach out to people you feel guilty and like a bad, absent friend ... but as soon as you DO interact with people, you spend the next 3 days dwelling on how  annoying you were & how they probably hate you now.
